SIMPLE: fated
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fated
<hw>Fat"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>p. p. & a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Decreed by fate; destined; doomed; <as>as, he was <ex>fated</ex> to
rule a factious people</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>One midnight⟦br⟧
<qex>Fated</qex> to the purpose.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Invested with the power of determining
destiny.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>fated</xex>
sky.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Exempted by fate.</def> <mark>[Obs. or R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fateful</ent>⟦br⟧
